# A person who does not eat [[animal]] [[flesh]], or in some cases, no animal products. There are several subcategories, see "related terms" below.
#* '''''Vegetarian''' – that’s an old Indian word for 'lousy hunter.' '' &mdash; Andy Rooney
# An animal that eats only plants, a [[herbivore]].

====Related terms====
*[[vegan]]: (''person who does not eat any animal products'')
*[[lactovegetarian]], [[lactarian]]: (''person who does not eat animal flesh but eats dairy products'') 
*[[lacto-ovo-vegetarian]], [[ovo-lacto-vegetarian]], [[ovolactovegetarian]]: (''person who does not eat animal flesh but eats other animal products'') 
*[[pescovegetarian]], [[pescetarian]], [[piscetarian]]: (''person who does not eat meat but does eat fish'')
*[[herbivore]]: (''the standard term used for a plant-eating animal'')

====Antonyms====
*[[carnivore]] 
*[[omnivore]]: (''animal eating meat and vegetable matter'')

